{"tid":1226070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔好怪班警員合情合理鎮壓你地班暴徒，係你班記者同埋暴徒一手一腳搞出黎","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:31:07.000Z","uid":174295,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bc93c8690f4bd1059daeec770b1b84b2b8625a","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"其實現場前線既警員都好危險！我係現場睇到班警員咁樣受傷睇到眼濕濕！<br />\n<br />\n佢地都承受住班十萬人既暴徒既暴力對待！連記者都加入暴徒陣型！<br />\n<br />\n所以我特意剪出警員合情合理合法制服現場暴徒既片段，歌頌一下佢地對香港和平穩定作出既無私奉獻！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/eiqKrnFMcVIDOAor5R/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FeiqKrnFMcVIDOAor5R%2Fgiphy.gif&h=18878651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場暴徒<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">施放隱形結界</span></strong>，圍毆警察，警員應聲倒地！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經送院後被證實腿部有0.0001% 永久修殘</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTutjsL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTutjsL.gif&h=345262b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名暴徒用Ｓ級忍術。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">嘴遁</span></strong>攻擊在場前線警員，警員神射手果斷一槍打爆暴徒個頭！好槍法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/bCXnqGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCXnqGY.gif&h=2448d161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現場記者施放閃光燈</span></strong>，導致一名警察<span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔到路仆街</span>英勇受傷！記者可恥！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQkxhT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQkxhT.png&h=41f86cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/NeUYizO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeUYizO.gif&h=1e6f2df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場前線記者再次無恥向警察施放閃光燈，英勇警察成功偷襲制止記者用相機襲擊警員！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/fX7plM00QX5FLwlNXP/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FfX7plM00QX5FLwlNXP%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e09f7201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者退卻後再次集結陣型，在場警員向記者擲向催淚彈催散，但係個催淚彈原來係現場暴徒淘寶返黎既假貨，原來示威者都有施放催淚彈！明顯有外國勢力干預！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/acaL6D5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacaL6D5.jpg&h=175a916c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線警員見暴徒施放美人計，前線指揮官擔心立法會外圍成為渣波魚蛋檣檔，特意拖去後排調教，將局勢穩定，警察做到野！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/FH392Ku.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFH392Ku.gif&h=226ca10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場有一名懷疑係恐怖份子企定定拎住一箱<span style=\"color: red;\">維他牌通明液體</span>，警員懷疑想發動<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自殺式炸彈製擊</span></strong>，迅速將恐怖份子以亂棍制服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/aCMfYij.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCMfYij.gif&h=6baac198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名現場警員怕射傷現場和平市民，<span style=\"color: red;\">特意在現場練靶</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/SLFDG8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLFDG8L.png&h=de180045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有暴徒企圖用救護車撞向警察陣型！速龍保持隊型，成功阻嚇救護車！如果唔係又要用真槍射救護車，現場指揮官愛民如子！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，如果有市民不幸比警員唔小心圍毆或射擊，都唔好怪班警員，佢地好多前線壓力太大導致患上思覺失調同埋被害妄想症，會唔小心以為喲人係到襲擊警察，請政府同埋777關注前線警員精神健康問題！請廣傳！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJgbVuq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJgbVuq.gif&h=897668bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n●一名在場警長不幸患上思覺失調，失控大呼：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好搞我後面！</span></strong>」，在場警員及市民均感愕然"},{"pid":"32b8ef3d391a3dc48f3c754865d7517c2d02e2c0","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d124c4420752115f064e3ddd517a36e65d5efa8","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d7fc8203d9c2044d975d34cf0e118f67befef8","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5840639f01192b480ca5c64bac3d257bedb381a5","tid":1226070,"uid":1303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻少少時間，希望可以入黎睇睇！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭之後，有更重要既事我地要去做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223305\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223305</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有無今次既事件都好，權力係會令人腐化，以前無濫權唔代表以後都唔會。<br />\n<br />\n任何既原因都唔應該成為「繞過法定守則去行使法律賦予你既特權」既基礎。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人養出黎隻狗仔率先去親身示範不守法，去示範點樣越過法例、特事特辦，後果絕對係災難性。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總有一日，朗朗乾坤，一片清明！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b44953b90207a07de469cf94e3c3147ba2cbd5","tid":1226070,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a42c9fe58eff7159a00abcbd0cc031c646a133c","tid":1226070,"uid":198199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"唔好怪警員呢5隻字照計一面倒全負皮至係...竟然6:0暫時好皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665a1956321618527a59900c8bbf38df762ff681","tid":1226070,"uid":52980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"哇你咁曲<br />\n好易按錯負評架嘛<br />\n<br />\n利申：正評"},{"pid":"cfe073897fabf50c9e9201fdeb456da39ea3d864","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"希望大家616大家一齊出黎關心前線警務人員精神健康問題!"},{"pid":"6bc73d47f5e7f72b9b5fc40c71c2d93317fe2c8d","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"665a1956321618527a59900c8bbf38df762ff681","tid":1226070,"uid":52980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"哇你咁曲<br />\n好易按錯負評架嘛<br />\n<br />\n利申：正評"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"乜野曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是直的，616出嚟關注警察精神健康問題！"},{"pid":"31d8c4dcb7d36b0231305660f49f97470f842fbd","tid":1226070,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9503d78b5e6e32cb5371b5253e5da47e4ae257c","tid":1226070,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"老老實實真係好撚僧你班標題黨<br />\n但係又忍唔住正評<br />\n<br />\nBTW 陣間誤導無入黎睇既人以為真係撐警察就好撚戇鳩囉"},{"pid":"061b5dabbb4dc90c10ec2fae0f68211c962947bc","tid":1226070,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,